 0 16 16" width="12" height="12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3.5 8.5 L7 12 L13 4.5"></path></svg>Beaucoup d&#x27;espace</span></div><p class="mt-2 text-[12px] leading-normal text-terroir-ink/[0.6]">Beaucoup d&#x27;espace par animal, faible chargement à l&#x27;hectare</p></div></div></div>"`;

